paragraph_text:
Retailers can purchase all our items direct from our website. You will find everything from sewing needles to scissors, plus a huge range of craft supplies for all creative projects. Our extensive range is updated constantly to include on-trend products sourced from local and international suppliers.
Birch Creative are the leaders in sourcing and distributing quality products for the craft and hobby industry. 
Inspiring ideas and handy tips to help you master your favourite craft. Whether you’re just starting out, or a seasoned professional, our printable how-to guides will show you how to create unique items, including home décor items, soft-as-anything baby blankets and bonnets, personalised gifts, and so much more. 
Birch head office in Heidelberg, Melbourne
Founded in 1926 by Edgar Birch, Birch Creative remains an Australian owned family company renowned for a comprehensive product range, and a commitment to developing strong relationships with retailers throughout the world, predominantly in Australia, New Zealand, Asia and the Pacific Islands.
What started as a single office in Melbourne’s Flinders Lane has expanded into an international company with over 22,000 products sourced from manufacturers all over the world.
